<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico"><link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
  <title>Create Event — GetRallied</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
    :root{--font:'Inter',sans-serif}
    body{font-family:var(--font);background:#fff;color:#111;min-height:100vh}
    .container{max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 24px 60px}
    h1{font-size:26px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.5px;margin-bottom:4px}
    .sub{color:#777;font-size:15px;margin-bottom:32px}
    .field{margin-bottom:20px}
    .field label{display:block;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#555;margin-bottom:6px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px}
    .field input,.field textarea,.field select{width:100%;padding:12px 14px;border:1.5px solid #e5e2dc;border-radius:6px;font-size:15px;font-family:var(--font);color:#111;background:#fff}
    .field input:focus,.field textarea:focus,.field select:focus{outline:none;border-color:#111}
    .field input::placeholder,.field textarea::placeholder{color:#bbb}
    .field textarea{resize:vertical;min-height:100px}
    .field .hint{font-size:12px;color:#aaa;margin-top:4px}
    .row{display:flex;gap:16px}
    .row .field{flex:1}
    .toggle-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:24px}
    .toggle-row input[type=checkbox]{width:18px;height:18px;accent-color:#111}
    .toggle-row label{font-size:14px;color:#555;font-weight:500}
    .btn-submit{width:100%;padding:15px;background:#111;color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:6px;font-size:16px;font-weight:800;font-family:var(--font);cursor:pointer;letter-spacing:-0.2px;transition:background .2s}
    .btn-submit:hover{background:#333}
    .btn-submit:disabled{opacity:0.6;cursor:not-allowed}
    .ai-note{background:#f7f6f4;border:1px solid #e5e2dc;padding:12px 16px;border-radius:6px;font-size:13px;color:#777;margin-bottom:28px;line-height:1.5}
    .ai-note strong{color:#111}
    @media(max-width:500px){.row{flex-direction:column;gap:0}}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/nav', { _navActive: 'dashboard' }) %>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Create a New Event</h1>
    <p class="sub">Describe what you need and AI will break it down into tasks.</p>

    <div class="ai-note">✨ <strong>How it works:</strong> Write your vision below — what you're organizing, what you need help with. Our AI will automatically break it into specific volunteer tasks with quantities.</div>

    <form method="POST" action="/create" id="create-form">
      <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= csrfToken %>">
      <input type="hidden" name="organizer_name" value="<%= account.name || '' %>">
      <input type="hidden" name="organizer_email" value="<%= account.email %>">

      <div class="field">
        <label>Event Title *</label>
        <input type="text" name="title" placeholder="e.g. Community Beach Cleanup, Block Party, Protest March" required>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label>Your Vision *</label>
        <textarea name="vision" placeholder="Describe what you're organizing and what kind of help you need. Be specific — the more detail, the better the task breakdown.&#10;&#10;Example: We're organizing a neighborhood cleanup day. We need people to pick up trash along the beach, someone to bring trash bags and gloves, a few people with trucks to haul debris, and someone to bring water and snacks for volunteers." required></textarea>
        <div class="hint">This is the magic part — describe your event and we'll create the volunteer task list.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="field">
          <label>Date</label>
          <input type="date" name="date" min="<%= new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0] %>">
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label>Location</label>
          <input type="text" name="location" placeholder="City, park, address...">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="toggle-row">
        <input type="checkbox" name="is_private" value="1" id="private-toggle">
        <label for="private-toggle">🔒 Make this event private (only people with the link can see it)</label>
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="btn-submit" id="submit-btn" onclick="this.disabled=true;this.textContent='Creating your event...';this.form.submit()">Create Event →</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
